　日\r\n　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　書　記　官　沈冠宇","JFULLPDF":"https://data.judicial.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/NHEM/111%2c%e6%b9%96%e7%b0%a1%2c414%2c20221028%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"NHEM,111,湖簡,414,20221028,1","JYEAR":"111","JCASE":"湖簡","JNO":"414","JDATE":"20221028","JTITLE":"竊盜"}